SELECT [t].[BookId], [t].[Author], [t].[Genre], [t].[ISBN], [t].[PublicationDate], [t].[Rating], [t].[Title], [r].[ReviewId], [r].[BookId], [r].[Rating], [r].[ReviewDate], [r].[ReviewText], [r].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT [b].[BookId], [b].[Author], [b].[Genre], [b].[ISBN], [b].[PublicationDate], [b].[Rating], [b].[Title]
    FROM [Books] AS [b]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
